  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0in 5.75pt 0in 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Weapon Preference: Missiles<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Research Preference: Speed &amp; Agility<o:p></o:p><=
/p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span> are an averag=
e-sized,
  canine species.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>For the <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span> their gre=
atest
  importance is wealth, they are always looking for a way to get rich fast =
and
  go to great risks to do so. Despite this desire, they generally don't
  consider taking riches from another being an option, being a mostly
  law-abiding race. Conversations with a <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span>
  generally just concentrate on what belongings they <span class=3DGramE>ha=
ve,</span>
  how big their homes are and other displays of wealth.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>For many <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span>, the daw=
n of the
  space age signals immense opportunity to become extremely rich. Early yea=
rs
  as a space-faring race saw large numbers of <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</=
span>
  launching themselves into the unknown in ill-equipped space craft, all for
  the opportunity to be one of the first to find riches beyond their world.=
<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span> are a bit war=
y of
  other races naturally but are usually very willing to trade. They are very
  dependable friends.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Cautious by nature the <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</=
span>
  have pioneered the ability to disrupt Hyperdrive use for a limited range =
in
  space.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>The Space Denial 500=
0S was
  developed as an early-warning system against planetary attacks by outside
  aggressors.<o:p></o:p></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span> live in small
  communities, where land is divided up by wealth. Border disputes are comm=
on
  and within their communities <span class=3DSpellE>Riktoh</span> will ofte=
n have
  fierce rivalries and few friendships.</p>
